ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:02:34.000Z","msg":"聽你講嘢似係絲打？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e60d0a62288f5bfd0fc1cdff2370492731c885","tid":1174346,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1498f72bd2e5833be2fe5683092386a0aaed0bad","tid":1174346,"uid":35481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T19:36:26.000Z","msg":"做野做到個個都鬧 做極都唔好<br />\n無人會睇你做岩幾多樣野，只會睇你做錯既幾樣野。<br />\n7年時間做呢一份工，發生兩件錯事就比人無限放大，<br />\n個個趁機借題發揮。<br />\n工作又係咁，感情又係咁。<br />\n晚晚失眠訓唔到，想食安眠藥但屋企又無。<br />\n每晚喊完諗完野諗住第二日無事，<br />\n但第二日又係咁，每日重複同一樣野。<br />\n好想有個出口解決自己，唔想再諗咁多。<br />\n<br />\n點解當我最需要你既時候你唔係比支持我，<br />\n而係同人地一樣鬧我，唔企係我呢邊諗。<br />\n而係同我講大把人慘過我，我呢啲好少事。<br />\n郁口埋口就話要自殺，要睇醫生。<br />\n叫我接受現實。<br />\n我同你求救但你無救我不特止仲要踩我。<br />\n我仲可以搵邊個幫我？<br />\n我唔想再繼續亂諗野諗到有日會做傻事，<br />\n我好想搵人求救但我發現無一個人幫我。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:53:26.000Z","msg":"看來你心中的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀．．．人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n <br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQRnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=8a74c9fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQRnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=00c42711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。</a> 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n <br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"1f94ff218516b5e3841f69bb4e3397383422b842","tid":1174346,"uid":35481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df7a050971dd7b50f8f67ba3caf403881d7bc973","tid":1174346,"uid":233397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:02:34.000Z","msg":"聽你講嘢似係絲打？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"我係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef1f3eff1d257ef5b8b5ab85f11f0c540aac514","tid":1174346,"uid":35481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:05:37.000Z","msg":"頭先有個frd叫我睇段李白既詞，<br />\n睇完之後自己寫左出黎。（字核突，唔好屌咁大力。）<br />\n但想講睇完李白呢篇詞，個心舒服左啲，<br />\n諗野都通左啲啲。<br />\n有啲事都係發生左，改變唔到任何人，就只可以改變自己心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n共勉之。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">希望陣間深夜得我一個既時候我都仲係咁識諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3COGT2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3COGT2b.png&h=60a16d81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e0b3bc9a170e9d7d8fbc30283f0ba92b6b45c5d","tid":1174346,"uid":35481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebc1ff78ee4f88ce934e808415c2bb8afead7878","tid":1174346,"uid":150575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:40:03.000Z","msg":"同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:07:52.000Z","msg":"同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你有咩打算？"},{"pid